description:
SOAP: Pobol y Cwm Omnibws
On: S4C Digital    
Date: Sunday 22nd December 2013 
Time: 17:00 to 18:50 

Catch up with all the week's events in Cwmderi in the omnibus edition. In Welsh with on-screen English subtitles.

Sad to hear about the loss of a Welsh tracker :(
Hope this helps those that might be stuck for Pobol y Cym. Also available at xtremetv.org.
